        <tr style="background:#f9fafb;"><td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #ddd;">Cherry blossom viewing</td><td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #ddd;">花見 (hanami)</td><td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #ddd;">Late March-April</td><td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #ddd;">Picnics under cherry trees with food, drinks, and friends</td></tr>
