        <tr style="background:#f9fafb;"><td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #ddd;">Year-end party</td><td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #ddd;">忘年会 (bounenkai)</td><td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #ddd;">December</td><td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #ddd;">End-of-year drinking party with coworkers to forget the year's troubles</td></tr>
